    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找失踪的女儿</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/472cf7fa735108de950fe81f76ac734b.poster.avif?t=1761897570\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/472cf7fa735108de950fe81f76ac734b.webm?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/472cf7fa735108de950fe81f76ac734b.mp4?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏是一个故事驱动的氛围恐怖体验，您的主要目标是在一家医院里找到失踪的女儿Clare。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着您的进展，您将揭开Clare的下落和医院里发生的黑暗秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集物品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/f22b0f1d54dfdcac99f7be8a4024c337.poster.avif?t=1761897570\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/f22b0f1d54dfdcac99f7be8a4024c337.webm?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/f22b0f1d54dfdcac99f7be8a4024c337.mp4?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，您需要收集各种物品，例如电池、弹药、武器、钥匙、拼图零件等。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与敌人战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/87011cb59121934cb917218e7d2be874.poster.avif?t=1761897570\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/87011cb59121934cb917218e7d2be874.webm?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/87011cb59121934cb917218e7d2be874.mp4?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您必须与医院中的一些敌人作斗争才能继续前进。这就是为什么你应该在医院里寻找弹药和武器。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >避开医生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/8aa935f6f3c7624f37f2a506782e734a.poster.avif?t=1761897570\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/8aa935f6f3c7624f37f2a506782e734a.webm?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/8aa935f6f3c7624f37f2a506782e734a.mp4?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，有一件事你无法射击或摧毁，那就是医生本人。或者你能吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解决难题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/46672d086a1db45499913f7f3e8e119f.poster.avif?t=1761897570\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/46672d086a1db45499913f7f3e8e119f.webm?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018430/extras/46672d086a1db45499913f7f3e8e119f.mp4?t=1761897570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，您需要找到物品（如钥匙）并解决逻辑难题才能继续前进。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发布计划</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们计划在今年（2024年）发布试玩版，并在明年（2025年）发布完整版游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏由两位来自匈牙利的游戏开发者制作。我们充满热情，在长时间的工作后将空闲时间投入到这个项目中，致力于让它成为现实。如果您对这款游戏感兴趣，您可以通过将它添加到您的愿望单来支持我们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们希望您会喜欢这款游戏！</p>",
